  - Add 2 parts:
    - Command to use private IP (like current)
    - Command to use for public IP
  - Command specifics:
    - The command should include sudo
    - The command should use /etc/kubernetes/admin.conf file
      - kubectl --kubeconfig /etc/kubernetes/admin.conf get po -A -owide

